<div class=3D"animationWrapper-QRL6aQ"></div></div></div></div><p>Additiona=
lly, it=E2=80=99ll be a lot easier for me to do more events and host meetup=
s for readers of this newsletter in the US. And I don=E2=80=99t just mean m=
eetups in New York. But across the country.</p><p>Multiple friends and read=
