tly, it occurred to me that homelessness and vagrancy doesn=E2=80=99t look =
so bad when you compare it to NY. The weather in LA is so great and the vib=
e is so chill that when you see a drug addict passed out on the sidewalk or=
 on the beach, you can think =E2=80=9COh, they=E2=80=99re just camping.=E2=
=80=9D</p><p>It=E2=80=99s a lot easier, faster, and more affordable to trav=
el from New York to California than London to California. So I=E2=80=99ll b=
e visiting the west coast more frequently. My mom and sister are happy abou=
t this. </p><p><span>There=E2=80=99s a lot to like about the UK, and it=E2=
=80=99ll continue to be a regular destination for me. Earlier this week, I =
attended a formal high table dinner at my old college (St Catharine=E2=80=
